'''Brent Edward Hefford''' (born [[8 May]], [[1978]]) is a [[New Zealand cricket team|New Zealand]] [[cricket]]er who plays for the [[Central Districts Stags]] in the [[State Championship]] and in the [[State Shield]]. He also plays for [[Marlborough cricket team|Marlborough]] in the [[Hawke Cup]] competition. He was born in [[Blenheim, New Zealand|Blenheim]].

